title: Parenthood ft. Navv Greene | Ep. 23
itunes:title: Parenthood ft. Navv Greene | Ep. 23
description:
The best fast food shift leader in the game aka Navv Green stops by the 85 South Show. He breaks down the ins & outs of the fast food industry and what it means to take hood strategy to the corporate world. DC also breaks the news of his first child on the way. Navv & Karlous give him some thoughts on what to look out for. Some of our in studio guests give some insight from the female perspective. Of course we let you know who this podcast is for. #85SouthShow

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
